title: LSU, Joe Burrow, winners & losers, and Tom Brady
itunes:title: LSU, Joe Burrow, winners & losers, and Tom Brady
description:
Colin discusses LSU's epic win last night, who the winners and losers are after their victory over Clemson, the journey of QB Joe Burrow, and why Tom Brady should stay in New England. Guests include Joel Klatt, Xavier Woods, Oliver Luck, DeForest Buckner, and Urban Meyer.
